{"tid":2146382,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"私隱公署指美國財政部公布香港官員個人資料明顯不必要","createTime":"2020-08-08T14:02:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T14:58:19.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f76b2d3e6a351e5a66c520c0d234643bafc66c10","tid":2146382,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T14:02:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542612-20200808.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542612-20200808.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiW2g5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=0f65b36a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542612-20200808.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=25239102\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542612-20200808.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n私隱專員公署表示，美國政府公布被制裁的香港官員及前官員的個人資料，明顯是過度披露和不必要，形同「起底」，對此十分失望。<br />\n<br />\n公署指，美國財政部的做法與數據道德期望完全背道而馳，過度披露個人資料可能會導致資料被非法使用，並對當事人造成極大滋擾。<br />\n<br />\n公署又指，聯邦公報猶如香港特區政府憲報，因此沒有由第三方要求移除内容的餘地，但公署會去信美國駐港澳總領事館、美國財政部及美國聯邦貿易委員會，對今次做法表達失望。"},{"pid":"48c1971258609499f6041d18b99110b3fe637ec4","tid":2146382,"uid":222970,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T14:03:53.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\"><strong>幫手retweet同比solomon睇</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ken_waikin/status/1292081869295464448?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fken_waikin%2Fstatus%2F1292081869295464448%3Fs%3D21&d=Ieu1u4uPL9fG%2BDPeYXLiW2g5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=46f52d45\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fken_waikin%2Fstatus%2F1292081869295464448%3Fs%3D21&h=90f95296\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ken_waikin/status/1